    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Slip behind the wheel and step back into an era of uncompromising elegance. This isn't just a motorcar; it\u2019s a preserved moment in history, finished in a deep, lustrous emerald that glows with a mirror-like finish. Inside, the heady scent of hand-stitched parchment leather and rich, glowing walnut veneers creates a sanctuary of silence, shielding you from the frantic modern world. Every curve of its iconic silhouette tells a story of prestige, and the engine hums with a refined, rhythmic whisper. This is a rare opportunity to own a masterpiece that has been cherished as a work of art, waiting for its next curator to continue its legendary journey.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
